column2: The kingdom of the Franks has long been disunited, but $SPHEREMASTER$ has finally decided that this is no longer the case. Their ruler has been crowned king of the Franks, and our people are clambering onto unite with them.
We don't exactly have a choice but to join them..

The kingdom of the Franks has not been united since the viking incursions in the 10th century, but we are in the position to take the crown. Delegations will be sent out to the petty kings and dukes of the land with a demand of subjugation. Francorum regnum iterum novum erit.
Our fatherland has been long divided. By combining the various Germanic peoples of Central Europe, we will forge a new German nation. Come, Germans!
We have created a strong country, but the continent is in disunity. We will become the guardian of this great southern land!
The future of our country is tied to this continent. We will make a new Korean realm!
Although our nation is younger than the Christian nations on this continent, we have secured our rightful territory and are in the position to conquer the continent. It is our destiny.
To the north and east of our continent lies an island chain that we should control.
